Prediction Assignement

Michael Garcia

August 26, 2018

Purpose

The purpose of this analysis is to develop a model that will predict the manner in which participants exercise. The study consists of 6 participants. Accelerometers on the belt, forearm, arm, and dumbell will provide the data.

Data Management

Due to the size, a SQLite db engine will be used to query the data

library(DBI)
# Create an ephemeral in-memory RSQLite database
con <- dbConnect(RSQLite::SQLite(), ":memory:")
dbWriteTable(con, "traindata", traindf)
dbWriteTable(con, "testdata", testdf)
trainres <- dbSendQuery(con, "SELECT * FROM traindata")
###trainres <- dbGetQuery(con,"select * from traindata")
dbFetch(res = trainres,n=10)
###dbClearResult(res)
##dbDisconnect(con)
